data.description: This charming property is nestled on 2.91 acres of picturesque Ideal location just 2 miles from the 401 bypass with easy access to Raleigh. The expansive lot offers plenty of space for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply enjoying the tranquility of nature.  Main house offers 2 bedrooms & 1 bath. As you step inside, you'll find the beautiful hardwood floors that flow seamlessly throughout most of the residence. The thoughtful updates have preserved the home's original charm while enhancing its functionality. 1-car garage, offering convenience & additional storage space. Whether you have a vehicle to park or need room for your hobbies, this garage provides the perfect solution. There is an additional dwelling unit, featuring 1 bedroom, a complete kitchen & living room, & a full bath. This separate living space can provide flexibility & potential income opportunities. Don't miss the chance to own this delightful.
